
	<div id="img">
		<p id="text">This piece is apart of a small Portfolio with a common theme: the unknown in a post-apocolyptic world. I love the genre of zombies and the apcolypse which I wanted to dive deeper in when creating this portfolio. I Never visually show zombies because I wanted my audience to feel a sense of eerieness and uncomfortability without knowing what was <i>truly</i> lurking in the shadows of this crumbled society. In this piece specifically, It shocases a guy an abandoned super market until he comes to a stop and  sees a shadowy figure linger at the entrance of the store.</p>
